&lt;li&gt;Own and manage complex timelines spanning development, production, post-production, and go-to-market execution.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with cross-functional stakeholders to identify risks, facilitate decisions, and maintain momentum across multiple concurrent initiatives.&lt;/li&gt;
